---
import homeHeroImage from '../assets/home-hero.png';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="About my blog"
	pubDate={new Date('May 18 2026')}
	heroImage={homeHeroImage}
>
	<style>
		/* Specifically targets the hero image rendered by the Layout on this page */
		:global(.hero-image img) {
			max-width: 480px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			display: block;
		}
	</style>
	<p>
		This is my new website! Hopefully I'm more active here. My posts will be a little old at first (written a couple years ago), but I will try to write new posts soon! Of course, I have new ideas and have a new perspective on a lot of things.
	</p>

</Layout>
